title: Ep 35: You have a bad smile
description:
Today's proceedings:  A officer who has a messy love life, a man is given a tough choice while on drugs, a fiancé with a terrible smile,  and someone asks what we are all wondering who is Elon Musk?  We also take an incredible test to determine the perfect Valentines date to take the Judgies out on.
